    <lb n="??"/>στρατ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ιώτου </supplied><gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/> </ab></div></div><div n="meta.17240" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.17240" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="107" notBefore="107" type="textDate" value="0107-03-26">26. März 107</date></p></div><div n="meta.17240" part="N" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Zur Datierung vgl. BL IV, S. 54 und VIII, S. 214 (mit unrichtig zitierter Datierung, vgl. die Quellenangabe). Vgl. Stauner, Schriftwesen, S. 427f., Nr. 420.</p></div><div n="meta.17240" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Mich.</title><biblScope type="volume">8</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">466</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">17240</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0163</series>; <biblScope type="volume">8</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">466</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0163;8;466" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.17240" part="N" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><listBibl><bibl type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">VIII</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">214/215</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">XI</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">132</biblScope></bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.17240" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.17240" part="N" subtype="otherPublications" type="bibliography"><head>Andere Publikation</head><bibl subtype="other" type="publication">Z. 42-45: C.Pap.Jud. III 486b</bibl></div><div n="meta.17240" part="N" subtype="translations" type="bibliography"><head>